<div class="color-1">
  <div class="billboard">
    <div class="container_16 clearfix">
      <div class="grid_11">
        <% link_to(tour_path) do %>
          <img src="/images/billboard-20100318.png" width="640" height="440" alt="Konichiwa!" />
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="grid_5 aligncenter" style="padding-top: 80px; line-height: normal;">
        <h1>No One Puts Music<br /> In A Corner.</h1>
        <h3>Bitspace is <em>a better way to store and listen to music</em>.
        Simply upload your collection and enjoy 
        it every day and from anywhere.</h3>
        <hr />
        <% if ENV['PRIVATE_BETA'] %>
          <% form_for InvitationRequest.new do |f| %>
            <h3>Subscribe for beta invite...</h3>
            <%= f.text_field :email, :class => 'required email', :hint => 'Enter your email address' %>
            <%= f.submit 'Subscribe' %>
            <%=h flash[:notice] %>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <div id="signup-button">
            <h3>
              <% link_to(price_path) do %>
                See Plans and Pricing →<br />
                <span>30-day free trial, sign up in 60 seconds</span>
              <% end %>
            </h3>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="color-2">
  <div class="container_16 clearfix">
    <div class="grid_16 aligncenter">
      <% case rand(3)
         when 0: %>
      <blockquote class="big-quote">
        <span class="start-quote">“</span>
        Bitspace is a game changer. It’s the finest example of a powerful, beautiful and standards-compliant web application.
        <span class="end-quote">”</span>
      </blockquote>
      - <a href="http://www.macstories.net/reviews/bitspace/" class="grey">MacStories.net</a>
      <% when 1: %>
      <blockquote class="big-quote">
        <span class="start-quote">“</span>
        Compared to Lala, Bitspace is definitely the prettier service and<br /> it's reliance on open web-standards is commendable.
        <span class="end-quote">”</span>
      </blockquote>
      - <a href="http://www.readwriteweb.com/archives/bitspace_html5_streaming_music_and_music_backup_services.php" class="grey">ReadWriteWeb</a>
      <% when 2: %>
      <blockquote class="big-quote">
        <span class="start-quote">“</span>
        For me, Bitspace is for music what Vimeo is for video.<br /> Simply amazing stuff.
        <span class="end-quote">”</span>
      </blockquote>
      - <a href="http://twitter.com/AnthonyMirelli/status/9950231866" class="grey">Twitter</a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="color-3">
  <div class="container_16 clearfix">
    <div class="grid_4">
      <h2>Store your<br />music collection</h2>
      <p><strong>External harddrives are slow, clunky, loud, ugly,
        inconvenient and tend to crash when you least expect it.</strong>
        Bitspace is nothing like a harddrive. It's beautiful, safe and just
        works. Easily and securely backup music that you have bought in
        your favorite online digital music store. That way you don't have
        to buy all your lost music again when your harddrive crashes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid_4">
      <h2>A better way to<br />organize music</h2>
      <p><strong>Tired of trying to keep your digital music library organized?</strong>
         Can't find the music you want when you need it? Or just want a good
         overview when you don't know what you want to listen to? We help you
         out by organizing the music for you. We make sure your meta data is
         correct and kept up to date, and we generate views
         that help you find music in a smart way.
    </div>
    <div class="grid_4">
      <h2>Always available<br />in the cloud</h2>
      <p><strong>Want to access your music from anywhere?</strong>
         Bitspace works just as well from home as behind a firewall at work. Your music library will always be available, no matter if you find yourself on a backstreet in Shibuya or on a beach in LA.
         There is no need for slow synchronizations between computers. You always have full
         access to all your favorite music, without worries.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid_4">
      <h2>HTML5 &ndash; for a better<br />and more useful web</h2>
      <p><strong>We use the latest web technologies in order to bring you the best
        possible product.</strong> With HTML5 we can utilize the native audio
        playback support in modern web browsers like Safari and Google Chrome.
        Bitspace can import and play pretty much all audio file formats
        in common use, like MP3, MP4, OGG, WMA and Flac with the click of a button.</p> 
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
